name: Six Gun
description:
This is an example of the "Six Gun" band. Each piece is 100% handmade, and one of a kind. As stated this is an EXAMPLE. All pieces are made to order, and will be made to fit your needs and style. (watch face not included). I will supply watch face for additional 20.00. This band features hand stitching as well as subtle tooled detail to the main strap. Also featured are two rivets made from real spent bullet shells, which are also hand made. These rivets are truely unique and are great accent to any band. 
Rivets can be added to any band or piece for an additional $5.00 ea.
